channel.title: Internet Companys in Wisconsin
channel.description: Hey everyone, I'm currently in the stages of upgrading my internet connection to my house because 6 laptops, 3 desktops, a Wii and 5 smart phones take up a lot of bandwidth. So my question is, anyone who lives in or close to the region, what is a good internet package? I currently have power boost from RoadRunner, which too be honest doesn't deserve that name at all. So yeah, any suggestions?
